{"tid":2186744,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"現階段遊行只係利用犧牲手足換取幾天關注，根本毫無意義。","createTime":"2020-09-03T07:24:10.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-01T10:20:34.000Z","uid":219007,"like":128,"dislike":60,"uniUserReply":41,"replies":[{"pid":"7ce9c69cf41d0559a7ab0dd3642b7cfb06c2d104","tid":2186744,"uid":219007,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-03T07:24:10.000Z","msg":"遊行肯定最少犧牲50-60名手足，七八成面臨監禁<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n但換來只係幾天的關注，之後生活照舊一樣、國際形勢照舊一樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n咁仲做黎做乜鳩？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n世界大戰都嚟緊<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n仲做呢啲嘢真係戇鳩鳩<br />\n<br />\n做下twitter戰線，鞏固黃色經濟圈效果肯定大過你一兩日遊行。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4877fb97ff85ee38490e79cbfcaabf37aa73be1f","tid":2186744,"uid":219007,"like":1,"dislike":8,"score":-7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-03T07:25:10.000Z","msg":"希望唔會有人咁容易衰衝動<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"90ed1b363cfb6013c3cbfc92ac6fdb298456b0d8","tid":2186744,"uid":215876,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-03T07:25:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ca9bd2cb4cca8319259cc4c75d569727996360ad","tid":2186744,"uid":320074,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-03T07:25:43.000Z","msg":"阿係，唔該杯葛吓依家飯民成日聲稱嘅「議會戰線」。"},{"pid":"b0192c934b5e2e7867cc06956ec1f3f7c1558905","tid":2186744,"uid"