明顯有政治傾向。而且敢出嚟嘅人實比以往少咗。所以出嚟嘅風險會大咗，要有一切心理準備。<br />\n<br />\n有啲人係怕咗國安法或疫情而唔敢出嚟，大家指責佢哋都唔會逼到佢哋出，甚至覺得畀人情緒勒索咗。會唔會有一啲方式，例如大規模走資易啲畀佢哋入口。"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-03T08:20:09.000Z","msg":"講到好似話走就可以走咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2c5c7bd757c1c472f7192f40ee5a567f2ce183a1","tid":2186744,"uid":169801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-03T08:20:45.000Z","msg":"你覺得做緊所謂國際線既接觸既人多，定國際報導接觸既人多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e3086f42262c5dd004e472b929b36d39429cefd6","tid":2186744,"uid":219007,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"4e997421abef025611b1bb6ef57d563a5ea0e132","tid":2186744,"uid":61569,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-03T08:17:39.000Z","msg":"你有咩高見?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-03T08:21:04.000Z","msg":"就算冇嘢做都唔代表一定要間硬搵啲嘢做<br />\n<br />\n你可以承認而家真係冇咩野做到<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"33feffb1d71127a630f0d4e7b279987e7a4dc7ad","tid":2186744,"uid":362865,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"aae7e951b5df58fee842aef7f566369178c94a74","tid":2186744,"uid":263618,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"b0192c934b5e2e7867cc06956ec1f3f7c1558905","tid":2186744,"uid":362865,"like":9,"dislike":10,"score":-1,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-09-03T07:26:26.000Z","msg":"「冇人出黎，天下太平，你說咩三道咩四」<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n你今日唔出黎，聽日你連twitter都冇得用"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-03T08:19:53.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-03T08:21:23.000Z","msg":"只係未到我，我冇遇過走得甩<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"706e0b92fff81a3cf0c6e4309e770d9d65902f8c","tid":2186744,"uid":275238,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-03T08:21:29.000Z","msg":"阿蛇又出嚟叫人唔好遊行呀？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class